<span id="fn_905"></span>[200:3](sbe31023.htm#fr_908.md) Observe the
impossibility of the meaning 'comfort,' or mere 'well-being' here.

<span id="fn_906"></span>[200:4](sbe31023.htm#fr_909.md) Or possibly 'the
